        "subject": "LU-15912 config: support autoconf 2.71",
        "message": "LU-15912 config: support autoconf 2.71\n\nautoconf 2.71 causes lots of deprecation warning and some errors.\n\"autoupdate\" can be used to update the files.\n\nThis patch is the result of running autoupdate, then cleaning up a\nbit.  It allows \"./configure\" to work on openSUSE Tumbleweed which\nhas 2.71\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Mr NeilBrown <neilb@suse.de>\nChange-Id: I4807d13d4db2e67d6c820b2a9c2eeab37aeca86d\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
